Dialogue: 10,0:01:54.10,0:01:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:57.92,0:01:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Aqui.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:02.93,0:02:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mestre?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:04.18,0:02:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,O que está fazendo?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:05.82,0:02:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Vim comprar umas tigelas pra mim,\N pra Touko-san e pro Shigeru-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:14.80,0:02:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Não vai comprar... a minha também?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.17,0:02:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Compre mais uma!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:23.17,0:02:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Levanta! Levanta logo, Natsume!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.81,0:02:36.58,Italics,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:37.18,0:02:39.26,Italics,,0,0,0,,Senti uma presença estranha...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.36,0:02:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Foi este quadro?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.60,0:03:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Te chamou a atenção?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.82,0:03:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Estou de saída, mas não vendi tudo.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.50,0:03:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Se quiser, pode levá-lo.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.88,0:03:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Vai pendurar?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.50,0:03:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,É só um monte de árvores secas, que pintura chata.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.17,0:03:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sério?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.40,0:03:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu até que achei bonito.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.58,0:03:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.38,0:03:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mas, é verdade...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.60,0:03:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Seria mais bonito se elas estivessem floridas.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.14,0:03:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,O que é isso?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.44,0:04:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,De onde elas vieram?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.21,0:04:22.36,Italics,,0,0,0,,Estranho...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.50,0:04:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,De novo?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.92,0:04:25.86,Italics,,0,0,0,,E na manhã seguinte...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.93,0:04:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoje de novo?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.86,0:04:35.12,Italics,,0,0,0,,No dia seguinte, havia mais pétalas no meu travesseiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.06,0:04:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Mestre, você não anda trazendo pétalas\N pra casa quando volta bêbado, não?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.26,0:04:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mas que audácia!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.92,0:04:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu nem gosto de flores!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.26,0:04:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Começou quando eu pendurei o quadro.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.69,0:04:55.73,Italics,,0,0,0,,Se é obra de algum Youkai, preciso agir logo.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.68,0:05:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Obrigada! É do tamanho que eu queria!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.44,0:05:04.06,Italics,,0,0,0,,Vou acabar com tudo que ameace este lar.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.96,0:05:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Não entre debaixo das minhas cobertas, Mestre!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.96,0:05:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Por que essa rede aí?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.82,0:05:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabia que isso tudo pode ser obra de fadas?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.78,0:05:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Vou tentar capturar uma!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.42,0:05:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Claro que essas coisas não existem.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.06,0:05:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Tem certeza disso?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.81,0:05:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Certeza absoluta? E aí, tem ou não?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.22,0:06:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Não gosto de invasores no meu território, senhorita.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.64,0:06:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Por que está deixando flores aqui?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.40,0:06:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,São uma oferenda para ele.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.09,0:06:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Você não tem nada a ver com isso.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.40,0:06:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Seu ladrão!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.24,0:06:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ladrão?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.12,0:06:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,O que foi que eu roubei?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.82,0:06:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sua insolente!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.36,0:06:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu vou te devorar!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.54,0:06:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Pare, Mestre!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.85,0:06:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Por quê?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.67,0:06:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,O que eu fiz?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.82,0:06:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Só estava tentando ser um bom guarda-costas...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.94,0:06:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Como assim, para ele?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.90,0:06:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Só tem eu e o Mestre aqui.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.96,0:06:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Do que está falando?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.09,0:06:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Veja, ele está bem ali.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.53,0:07:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Não grite.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.45,0:07:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,O Yasaka-sama vai se assustar.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.21,0:07:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, c-claro...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.83,0:07:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,O resto da casa também...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.02,0:07:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yasaka-sama?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.34,0:07:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.49,0:07:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ele mora nesse quadro.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.92,0:07:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Vou levá-lo comigo.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.42,0:07:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ele pertence a mim.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.92,0:07:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Fui descuidada e um humano o roubou,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.02,0:07:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,e agora ele veio parar nesta casa miserável.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.28,0:07:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Esta... casa...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.98,0:07:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Não quer sair!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.35,0:07:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.35,0:07:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Não sai mesmo...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.52,0:07:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Você pregou ele na parede?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.73,0:07:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Claro que não!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.14,0:07:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,O que você aprontou com ele, hein?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.37,0:07:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.13,0:07:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Não tenho escolha.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.26,0:08:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Voltarei aqui toda noite até o quadro sair.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.24,0:08:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.54,0:08:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu me chamo Miya. Voltarei amanhã.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.85,0:08:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Espere!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.00,0:08:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Não deixe essa coisa bizarra aqui!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.84,0:08:15.46,Italics,,0,0,0,,E conforme ela disse...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.01,0:08:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Com licença.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.69,0:08:23.04,Italics,,0,0,0,,A Miya voltou no dia seguinte.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.62,0:08:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Me dê sua mão, garoto.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.25,0:08:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Em agradecimento por cuidar do Yasaka-sama.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.60,0:08:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu agradeço, mas pare de espalhar pelo quarto!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.00,0:08:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ei, voltem aqui!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.48,0:08:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,São bonitas, né?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.74,0:08:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,O Yasaka-sama originalmente era humano.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.05,0:08:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ele adorava observar flores e borboletas.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.38,0:08:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ele era... humano?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.66,0:09:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,É uma história antiga...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.77,0:09:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu estava no topo de uma cerejeira observando as flores.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.97,0:09:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Quando elas floresciam, me traziam uma sensação de paz.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.85,0:09:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu estava feliz, então escondida nas flores, tentei conversar com ele.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.84,0:09:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Você gosta mais do livro do que das pétalas de cerejeira?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.72,0:09:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ficar vendo palavras é mais divertido que ver as flores?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.21,0:09:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosto de livros e de flores.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.80,0:09:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,E gosto de conversar com você.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.93,0:09:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ele me disse que se chamava Yasaka,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.15,0:09:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,e que, mesmo enfermo, tinha pouco tempo para si,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.86,0:09:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,porque era o herdeiro de uma família rica.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.97,0:10:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ele nunca percebeu que eu era um Ayakashi,\N e conversou comigo várias vezes.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.41,0:10:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Mas...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.80,0:10:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu tinha medo que ele descobrisse quem sou.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.80,0:10:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Então eu só frequentava aquele jardim\N quando havia pétalas para me esconder.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.48,0:10:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Éramos amigos que só conversavam durante a primavera.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.56,0:10:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Miya.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.12,0:10:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Se algum dia eu for livre, quero poder viajar pelo mundo todo.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.25,0:10:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenho certeza que existem outros campos maravilhosos de flores.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.26,0:10:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Miya, por que será?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.10,0:10:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenho tanta coisa que gostaria de te contar.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.86,0:10:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Certo ano, depois do fim da primavera,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.10,0:10:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,ele subitamente parou de vir.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.32,0:10:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu esperei e esperei...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.25,0:10:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Até a próxima primavera,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.74,0:10:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,e a primavera seguinte.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:01.64,0:11:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Procurei ele por todo canto.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.77,0:11:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Não sabia onde ele poderia estar. Procurei por toda parte.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.58,0:11:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Até que, então...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.64,0:11:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,encontrei o quadro.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.60,0:11:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Me disseram que um famoso Ayakashi artista o pintou.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.80,0:11:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Talvez ele estivesse insatisfeito com\N o mundo e fugiu para o quadro.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.50,0:11:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Foi por isso que depois que comprei o quadro, viajei com ele para fazê-lo feliz.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.08,0:11:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Para que, um dia, quando o coração dele estivesse em paz, ele saísse dali.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.42,0:11:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,E finalmente eu poderia conversar de novo com ele.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.16,0:11:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,É verdade que este quadro foi \Npintado por um famoso artista Ayakashi.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.25,0:12:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mas é só um quadro.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.42,0:12:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,É só um quadro de cerejeiras no inverno,\N com esse tal de Yasaka pintado no meio.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.52,0:12:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ela pode esperar o quanto quiser que ele não vai sair.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.13,0:12:18.80,Italics,,0,0,0,,Mesmo assim, a Miya trazia flores todos os dias.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.52,0:12:20.42,Italics,,0,0,0,,Todos os dias...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.76,0:12:21.97,Italics,,0,0,0,,Todos os dias...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.36,0:12:23.21,Italics,,0,0,0,,Todos os dias...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.05,0:12:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Que tosse estranha a sua.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.43,0:12:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,E não para...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.82,0:12:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ei, Mestre.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.07,0:12:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Não pisoteie as flores.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.33,0:12:58.97,Italics,,0,0,0,,Então a Miya viajou o mundo, procurando por belas paisagens, e carregando apenas um quadro?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.21,0:13:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Perdão. Perdão.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.39,0:13:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Esse é o Harujizou.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.10,0:13:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ele é um Ayakashi que aparece durante a primavera e prevê o futuro das pessoas,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.69,0:13:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Uma sombra maligna o persegue.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.44,0:13:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Vejo uma árvore brotando do seu corpo.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.80,0:13:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Espere!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.60,0:13:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Como assim, meu corpo?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.83,0:13:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Takashi-kun?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.29,0:13:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Touko-san?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.32,0:13:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,O que foi?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.59,0:13:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Por que está aí gritando para o nada?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.92,0:13:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Eu não...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.40,0:13:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Não era nada.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.52,0:13:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sério?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.77,0:13:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.18,0:13:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Certo...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.98,0:14:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.69,0:14:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Certo, vamos para casa?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.57,0:14:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.57,0:14:12.53,Italics,,0,0,0,,"Estava com medo que ele descobrisse o que sou."
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.41,0:14:14.22,Italics,,0,0,0,,Sim...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.91,0:14:17.32,Italics,,0,0,0,,Sou igual a ela.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.85,0:14:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Cara, o que foi aquilo?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.30,0:14:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As palavras daquele Harujizou...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.81,0:14:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.76,0:14:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mas que diabos?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.77,0:14:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Já sei!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.94,0:14:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Descobri de onde vem sua tosse!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.96,0:14:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,O quadro está drenando sua energia,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.52,0:14:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,e está se ramificando para drenar ainda mais!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.20,0:14:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mestre?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.95,0:14:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Nenhum quadro vai roubar a minha presa!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.58,0:14:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Vou devorá-lo agora!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.87,0:14:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Pare, Mestre!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.29,0:15:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Esse quadro é da Miya...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.71,0:15:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume, seu idiota!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.96,0:15:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Por que fez isso?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.96,0:15:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Levanta, seu imbecil!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.73,0:15:21.58,Italics,,0,0,0,,Miya.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.64,0:15:25.66,Italics,,0,0,0,,Se algum dia eu for livre, quero poder viajar pelo mundo todo.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.23,0:15:28.98,Italics,,0,0,0,,Mas não posso ir sozinho.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.36,0:15:31.37,Italics,,0,0,0,,Você me acompanharia?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.90,0:15:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Olá, Miya.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.16,0:15:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Veio me ver esse ano também?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.28,0:15:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Quer conversar sobre o quê?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.38,0:15:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Desculpe, Natsume.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.41,0:15:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,De tanto carregar o quadro, ele absorveu energia espiritual.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.21,0:16:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ele não sai da parede porque está enraizado.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.52,0:16:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sua vida está correndo perigo.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.77,0:16:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,O jeito será usar o poder que me resta para queimá-lo.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.36,0:16:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Não faça isso, Miya!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.07,0:16:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ele é importante pra você, não é?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.40,0:16:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Tudo bem, Natsume.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.00,0:16:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A verdade é que eu percebi...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.77,0:16:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Que ele...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.33,0:16:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Que o Yasaka-sama... já se foi.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.52,0:16:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Mas eu aproveitei as viagens que tive com esse quadro como se estivesse viajando com ele.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.50,0:16:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Nos dias de chuva...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.64,0:16:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Nos dias com vento...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.10,0:16:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Nunca estive sozinha.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.09,0:16:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mas...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.40,0:16:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Já basta.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.62,0:17:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Só queria conversar de frente com ele, sem\N me importar em como me pareceria para ele.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.88,0:17:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Miya...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.17,0:17:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu ainda estou bem.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.63,0:17:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos descobrir juntos uma maneira de tirá-lo daí.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.05,0:17:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mas...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.98,0:17:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Também gosto deste quadro.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.52,0:17:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiotice...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.29,0:17:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A Miya é igual a mim, Mestre.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.73,0:17:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Temos medo só de pensar em contar a verdade\N para quem é importante e ficamos tristes.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.09,0:17:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Desculpe, Mestre.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.44,0:17:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mas eu quero que a Miya fique com o quadro.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.28,0:17:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu sei que o Yasaka-sama está nele.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.30,0:17:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ele queria te ver, mesmo sabendo que você não apareceria num dia de inverno.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.33,0:17:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,O Yasaka-sama está procurando por você, Miya.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.42,0:17:57.08,Italics,,0,0,0,,Porém, mesmo depois de vários dias, não achamos uma solução.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.44,0:18:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Pelo menos a Touko-san não consegue ver os ramos.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.66,0:18:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiota.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.37,0:18:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Estou decidida.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.17,0:18:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Vou queimá-lo.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.05,0:18:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Miya?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.34,0:18:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mas antes disso, quero fazer as árvores do quadro florescerem.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.22,0:18:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Como no dia em que eu o conheci.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.55,0:18:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Pode me ajudar?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.96,0:19:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Terminamos.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.47,0:19:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.54,0:19:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Que bonito...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.30,0:19:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Miya...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.82,0:19:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Miya...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.30,0:19:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,O Yasaka-sama...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.81,0:19:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Obrigada, Natsume.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:40.69,0:19:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Boa noite.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.66,0:19:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Boa noite.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.61,0:20:00.18,Italics,,0,0,0,,Entendi... Estou dentro do quadro...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.88,0:20:43.33,Italics,,0,0,0,,Quando acordei, os ramos do quadro e\N as pétalas que pintamos tinham sumido.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.57,0:20:49.77,Italics,,0,0,0,,Olhei dentro do quadro, mas não vi o Yasaka-sama ali.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.21,0:20:55.37,Italics,,0,0,0,,Mal encostei nele e o quadro saiu da parede.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.58,0:21:01.30,Italics,,0,0,0,,E desde aquele dia, nunca mais vi a Miya.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.82,0:21:08.58,Italics,,0,0,0,,Miya, acho que a alma dele veio mesmo morar no quadro.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.61,0:21:13.04,Italics,,0,0,0,,E o quadro absorvia minhas energias
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.54,0:21:17.96,Italics,,0,0,0,,para tentar fazer as flores desabrocharem e te ver de novo.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.70,0:21:23.42,Italics,,0,0,0,,Será que eles estão cobertos de pétalas?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.41,0:21:29.36,Italics,,0,0,0,,Ou será que ele saiu do quadro e estão viajando juntos?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.01,0:21:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Takashi-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.70,0:21:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Será que a Miya lhe contou a verdade?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.08,0:21:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Disse algo, Natsume?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.40,0:21:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Nada não, Mestre.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.93,0:21:56.71,Italics,,0,0,0,,Adeus, Miya.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:59.40,0:22:02.04,Italics,,0,0,0,,Minha amiga que conheci na estação das flores.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:36.66,0:23:38.50,Italics,,0,0,0,,Desde que vi aquelas estranhas pegadas,
Dialogue: 10,0:23:38.50,0:23:40.68,Italics,,0,0,0,,coisas estranhas começaram a acontecer em casa.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:40.85,0:23:43.10,Italics,,0,0,0,,Parece até algo que aconteceu quando eu era pequeno.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:43.10,0:23:44.00,Italics,,0,0,0,,Shigeru-san...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:44.15,0:23:46.77,Italics,,0,0,0,,Mas tudo acabou com a vinda daquela pessoa.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:46.77,0:23:50.05,Italics,,0,0,0,,Era uma garota estranha, mas muito bonita.
